">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 5282, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 630458, "username": "jianyang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jianyang", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b7fd/daca/630458_mini.png?m=1695887675", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b7fd/daca/630458_normal.png?m=1695887675", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b7fd/daca/630458_large.png?m=1695887675", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b7fd/daca/630458_xlarge.png?m=1695887675", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b7fd/daca/630458_xlarge.png?m=1695887675", "created": 1684845529, "last_modified": 1695887675}, "last_reply_by": "stevenzhang13", "last_touched": 1731188797, "title": "mac 剪切板 APP 有推荐吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1087989", "created": 1731131276, "deleted": 0, "content": "用了 maccy 能用，但有 bug\r\n我有时候用 PD 虚拟机，经常用快捷键启动 maccy 。有时候不能复制，要重复选择复制项好几次才生效，有时候快捷键启动的时候 APP 会卡死，只能强制结束进程关闭。\r\n\r\n看到有人推荐 pastenow ， 价格还行 50R 买断， 这个 APP 问题多吗？\r\n\r\n或者有其他买断制的 APP 推荐吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>用了 maccy 能用，但有 bug\n我有时候用 PD 虚拟机，经常用快捷键启动 maccy 。有时候不能复制，要重复选择复制项好几次才生效，有时候快捷键启动的时候 APP 会卡死，只能强制结束进程关闭。</p>\n<p>看到有人推荐 pastenow ， 价格还行 50R 买断， 这个 APP 问题多吗？</p>\n<p>或者有其他买断制的 APP 推荐吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1731131276, "replies": 57, "id": 1087989}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27244, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3061, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 285326, "username": "eachann", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/eachann", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64b4/e24e/285326_mini.png?m=1731123595", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64b4/e24e/285326_normal.png?m=1731123595", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64b4/e24e/285326_large.png?m=1731123595", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64b4/e24e/285326_xlarge.png?m=1731123595", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64b4/e24e/285326_xlarge.png?m=1731123595", "created": 1516603708, "last_modified": 1731123595}, "last_reply_by": "xiely", "last_touched": 1731178936, "title": "m4 mini 连夜装完后索然无味", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1087965", "created": 1731124162, "deleted": 0, "content": "| 把 Docker 搞完，把 mbp 用的软件对着重新装一次，搞到 2 点多后索然无味了\r\n\r\n功耗确实不高，加上我这边路由器、手表充电器加起来才一共 16-20w 的样子\r\n\r\n当时为了把 m4 mini 打造成 nas 还把极空间的 z4 pro 出了，折腾完后我发现我其实对 nas 也没有很大需求 （尴尬）\r\n\r\n\r\n家里没电脑的用户可能有需求？但是家里没电脑的用户把，这么久也没买电脑说明也可能不是刚需？", "content_rendered": "<p>| 把 Docker 搞完，把 mbp 用的软件对着重新装一次，搞到 2 点多后索然无味了</p>\n<p>功耗确实不高，加上我这边路由器、手表充电器加起来才一共 16-20w 的样子</p>\n<p>当时为了把 m4 mini 打造成 nas 还把极空间的 z4 pro 出了，折腾完后我发现我其实对 nas 也没有很大需求 （尴尬）</p>\n<p>家里没电脑的用户可能有需求？但是家里没电脑的用户把，这么久也没买电脑说明也可能不是刚需？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1731124162, "replies": 53, "id": 1087965}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c81e/728d/2_large.png?m=1716587234", "name": "v2ex", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c81e/72